+        - FlashAttention: kv_cache shape [2, num_blocks, block_size, num_kv_heads, head_size]
+        - FlashInfer:     kv_cache shape [num_blocks, 2, block_size, num_kv_heads, head_size]
+
+        We pin host memory (`pin_memory=True`) so the H2D copy on recall is
+        DMA-able and async-friendly. Per-layer capture is sequential here;
+        if a single capture-op spans many blocks it is still O(num_blocks)
